column4: I hate to be a bother but if someone could perhaps whisper me with their solution I'd appreciate it as I find it hard to follow the thread in a busy chatroom

when checking my alsa panel, under switches it only shows iec958 and headphone
any ideas on how to get my main speaker port to show?
all channels that I can see have been unmuted
